    "Title": "BlacJac Bounty Trial Contract",
    "Description": "ATTN: Bounty Hunters\n\nNot sure if you\u2019re interested, but BlacJac is looking to expand our roster of bounty hunters. We got more jobs than our current contractors can handle, so I\u2019m hoping that you might be able to help pick up some of the slack.  \n\nYour qualifications look good on paper, but before we make anything official, BlacJac needs to see how you perform in the field firsthand. Even got a test case all lined up \u2013 we want you to sort out ~mission(TargetName). They were last seen at ~mission(Location|Address). Should be a fairly straightforward bounty without too much resistance. Perfect thing to sharpen your teeth on.\n\nGood luck,\nGloria Mesa\n\nPrivate Contract Supervisor\nBlacJac Security, \"Protection Provided\"",
